spec_data.Name: perl-Sort-Naturally
spec_data.Description:
This module exports two functions, 'nsort' and 'ncmp'; they are used in
implementing my idea of a "natural sorting" algorithm. Under natural
sorting, numeric substrings are compared numerically, and other
word-characters are compared lexically.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 04:02:01 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Sort lexically, but sort numeral parts numerically
